long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: MIX Click2Call is a browser extension for Google Chrome that recognizes phone numbers on any web page and presents them as clickable links.  Once a number is clicked, it initiates a call with your MIX PBX extension and dials out from your registered device.
